longBusinessSummary: Hero Technologies Inc., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of oil and gas properties in Australia. It holds a working interest in two petroleum exploration licenses (PELs), including a 48.5003% working interest in PEL 112 covering 1,086 square kilometers; and a 53.3336% working interest in PEL 444 covering 1,166 square kilometers located on the southwestern flank of the Cooper Basin in the state of South Australia. The company was formerly known as Holloman Energy Corporation and changed its name to Hero Technologies Inc. in July 2020. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Houston, Texas. Hero Technologies Inc. is a subsidiary of Holloman Corporation.
